@PreAuthorize(&quot;#userSubject == #auth.token.claims[&#39;sub&#39;]&quot;)
public ResponseEntity&lt;String&gt; addAnswer(@PathVariable(&quot;subject&quot;) String userSubject, @RequestBody @Valid AnswerDto, JwtAuthenticationToken auth) {
     ...
}
```

